						<text>
							Playing possum! Opossum&#8217;s are famous for playing possum when threatened by predators like a fox or bobcat, opossums sometimes flop on their side and lie on the ground with their eyes closed and tongue out &#8211; looking like they are dead. They will sometimes even foam at the mouth! This ploy confuses predators and once the opossum is free he gets back up and goes about his day.
